<h2>Good news, {{ user.first_name }}!</h2>

<p>
Your listing, '<a href="{{ listing.listing_url }}">{{ listing.name }}</a>' at {{ listing.street }}, was just booked!
</p>

<div class="booking-details">

  <div class="row">
    <strong style='display: inline-block;'>Who</strong>
    <span style="float: right;"><a href="{{ reservation.owner.user_profile_url }}">{{ reservation.owner.first_name }}</a></span>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <strong style='display: inline-block;'>What</strong>
    <span style="float: right;"><a href="{{ listing.listing_url }}">{{ listing.name }}</a> x {{ reservation.quantity }}</span>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <strong style='display: inline-block;'>When</strong>
    <span style="float: right;">
      {% if listing.hourly_reservations? %}
        {{ reservation.hourly_summary }}
      {% else %}
        {{ reservation.dates_summary }}
      {% endif %}
    </span>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <strong style='display: inline-block;'>Total</strong>
    <span style="float: right;">{{ reservation.total_price }}</span>
  </div>

</div>

<p>Exciting, right? Please, confirm the booking and let's get the guest set up!</p>

<a class="btn" href="{{ reservation.reservation_confirm_url_with_tracking | append:signature_for_tracking }}">Confirm Booking</a>

<p>Not ready for guests? You can manage your bookings <a href="{{ listing.manage_guests_dashboard_url }}">here</a>.</p>

<p>If you need help, send an email to <a href="mailto:happydesk@desksnear.me">happydesk@desksnear.me</a> or contact us at {{ platform_context.phone_number }}.</p>
